# 6. Azure AD Group Mapping

Map Azure AD Groups to application roles.

Configuration must come from properties/environment variables.

Example:

```
ROLE_VIEWER_GROUP

ROLE_EDITOR_GROUP

ROLE_ADMIN_GROUP
```

No hardcoded group IDs.

